snippet.title: Wreckfest - Banger Racing Car Pack Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://order.wreckfestgame.com/

Car Pack number 6 is out, which concludes Season Pass #1 in terms of content. Will there be a Season Pass #2 you wonder? We sure as hell think so, yes, but stay tuned for more official info down the line. Included in this car pack are 3 amazing cars, and we are not saying this in your standard car salesman voice, no, this comes directly from our engines. There is the Sweeper, the Hearse, and the Stock Car. 

New car? Check! 
New Style? Check 
New You? We don't know, honestly... 

Furthermore, a new tournament month has started with new in-game swag.

Wreckfest has cars in it that either crash in each other while they race, or just crash in each other for the pure fun of it. It really is awesome, so check it out if you want to. If not: we're not mad.
---
Website: https://order.wreckfestgame.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/wreckfest
PS4: http://n.thq.com/2B0Q30pvFwZ
#Wreckfest #DriveHardDieLast
